<div style="width: min(1200px, 90%); margin: auto;">
  <h2 class="title-center">Hover Over Each AQI Category to Learn More</h2>
  <ul style="display: flex; gap: 1rem;  flex-wrap: wrap; list-style: none; padding: 1rem 0.5rem;">
    <li class="aqi-btn good-active">
        AQI 0 - 50
    </li>
    <li class="aqi-btn moderate">
        AQI 51 - 100
    </li>
    <li class="aqi-btn sensitive">
        AQI 101 - 150
    </li>
    <li class="aqi-btn unhealthy">
        AQI 151 - 200
    </li>
    <li class="aqi-btn very-unhealthy">
        AQI 201 - 300
    </li>
    <li class="aqi-btn hazardous">
        AQI 301 - 500
    </li>
  </ul>
  <ul style="list-style: none; margin-bottom: -1rem;">
    <li class="aqi-description show">
      <div class="aqi-description-content">
        <p style="color: var(--good);">AQI 0-50</p>
        <p class="aqi-level-text">GOOD</p>
        <p>Air quality is considered satisfactory, and air pollution poses little or no risk.</p>  
      </div>
      <div class="aqi-image">
        <img
          width="100%"
          src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0622/1715/8830/files/WYND_Plus_tracker.jpg?v=1661356024" 
        />
      </div>
    </li>
    <li class="aqi-description hide">
      <div class="aqi-description-content">
        <p style="color: var(--moderate);">AQI 51-100</p>  
        <p class="aqi-level-text">MODERATE</p>  
        <p>Air quality is acceptable: however, for some pollutants 
          there may be a moderate health concern for a very small 
          number of people who are unusually sensitive to air pollution.
        </p>  
      </div>
      <div class="aqi-image">
        <img
          width="100%"
          src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0622/1715/8830/files/WYND_Plus_tracker-fair.jpg?v=1661356024" 
        />
      </div>
    </li>
    <li class="aqi-description hide">
      <div class="aqi-description-content">
        <p style="color: var(--sensitive);">AQI 101-150</p>  
        <p class="aqi-level-text">UNHEALTHY FOR SENSITIVE GROUPS</p>  
        <p>Members of sensitive groups may experience health effects. The general public is not likely to be affected.</p>  
      </div>
      <div class="aqi-image">
        <img
          width="100%"
          src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0622/1715/8830/files/WYND_Plus_tracker-moderate.jpg?v=1661356023" 
        />
      </div>
    </li>
    <li class="aqi-description hide">
      <div class="aqi-description-content">
        <p style="color: var(--unhealthy);">AQI 151-200</p>  
        <p class="aqi-level-text">UNHEALTHY</p>  
        <p>Everyone may begin to experience health effects, members of sensitive groups may experience more serious health effects.</p>  
      </div>
      <div class="aqi-image">
        <img
          width="100%"
          src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0622/1715/8830/files/WYND_Plus_tracker-bad.jpg?v=1661356024" 
        />
      </div>
    </li>
    <li class="aqi-description hide">
      <div class="aqi-description-content">
        <p style="color: var(--very-unhealthy);">AQI 201-300</p>  
        <p class="aqi-level-text">VERY UNHEALTHY</p>  
        <p>Health alert: everyone may experience more serious health effects.</p>  
      </div>
      <div class="aqi-image">
        <img
          width="100%"
          src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0622/1715/8830/files/WYND_Plus_tracker-hazardous.jpg?v=1661356023" 
        />
      </div>
    </li>
    <li class="aqi-description hide">
      <div class="aqi-description-content">
        <p style="color: var(--hazardous);">AQI 301-500</p>  
        <p class="aqi-level-text">HAZARDOUS</p>  
        <p>Health warnings of emergency conditions. The entire population is more likely to be affected.</p>  
      </div>
      <div class="aqi-image">
        <img
          width="100%"
          src="//cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/1413/8998/files/WYND_Plus_tracker-hazardous2_1024x1024_b913f512-0641-40d6-b64f-03b368912698_1024x1024.webp?v=1650920379" 
        />
      </div>
    </li>
  </ul>
</div>


{% schema %}
  {
    "name": "Aqi Categories",
    "settings": []
  }
{% endschema %}

{% stylesheet %}

